@startuml
title Architecture Finalization Sequence

actor Architect
participant "Review Pack" as RP
participant "Traceability Matrix" as TM
participant "Release Notes" as RN
participant "Repository" as Repo

Architect -> RP : Review volumes and ADRs
RP -> TM : Validate principle-to-artifact mapping
TM -> RN : Confirm release criteria
Architect -> Repo : Approve release candidate
Repo -> RN : Publish EARA v1.0.0 notes
@enduml
